[normal]Patricia A Whelan – Written evidence[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Ref: Upcoming Deregulation Bill, in particular Green Lanes
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]All unsealed BOATs and UCRs should be reclassified as RESTRICTED BYWAYS.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]I am a member of Yorkshire Dales Local Access Forum and of N.Yorkshire LAF and a member of the British (Horse) Driving Society and am very aware of the problems caused by motorised vehicles – mainly motorcycles on ‘green lanes’.  
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]I hope that you will consider my submission when assembling forthcoming Deregulation Bill.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Thank you for your attention.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
